(51, 'Smart radio + WLAN gate control ND-GC-1S SET with 2 hand transmitters', 'Fully automatic with radio and app control', 'Automatic gate, opens and closes fully automatically', 'Universally applicable and therefore suitable for every goal', 'Easy configuration and control via app - Android, IOS, Windows', 'Integrated lighting control, ventilation control and intruder alarm', 'Made in Germany', '30 days return policy', '', 'Model selection', 'ND-GC-1S + 2 hand transmitters', '<p>NODEMATIC® WLAN and radio gate control ND-GC-1S - automatic control, designed for universal use in gate systems</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product advantages of our smart gate control / garage door control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Parameterization complete via app -&gt; No more complicated menus, DIP switches or jumpers!<br />\r\nno additional smart home center / HUB necessary<br />\r\nComfort functions such as fully automatic closing or opening via geofencing, intruder alarm, autonomous ventilation position are already integrated and can be easily personalized with an app and are immediately ready for use<br />\r\nControl your garage door conveniently using the on-site control button, radio hand-held transmitter or worldwide using an app</p>\r\n\r\n<p>highlights</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Universally applicable: Can be used in gate systems, e.g<br />\r\nFree app for Android, IOS and Windows<br />\r\nRemote control: control via control button, radio transmitter or worldwide via app. Receive notifications* or get the current gate position at any time<br />\r\nInnovative and fully automatic: Your smart gate opens fully automatically (geofencing)* - it is open just when you get home. Perfect for motorcyclists or if you forgot the handheld transmitter. It closes automatically when you drive away or forget to close it. You will be alerted if the gate is opened by force or you can switch on the lights. It moves into the ventilation position to protect your vehicle from getting wet<br />\r\nEasy installation: Fully configurable via a free app (Android, IOS and Windows), so new devices can be easily added via QR code, settings can be adjusted or hand-held transmitters can be taught. No programming knowledge is necessary. Detailed operating and installation instructions are included with the intelligent control. Use even without WLAN thanks to the wireless access point<br />\r\nModern additive manufacturing - Made in Germany: Our components are precisely manufactured using the 3D printing process. This makes our hand-held transmitters uniquely light and ultra-compact</p>\r\n\r\n<p>functions and equipment</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Engine shutdown per runtime [1 - 300s]<br />\r\nMotor shutdown via external limit switch<br />\r\nUp to 50 hand-held transmitters can be taught, fix code EV1527 + rolling code<br />\r\nlighting control<br />\r\nControl several gates at the same time via widget*<br />\r\nAutomatically open/close via geofencing*<br />\r\nAutomatic closing [1 - 30min]<br />\r\nIntruder alarm<br />\r\nventilation position<br />\r\nnotifications*<br />\r\nUser Permissions: Installer WiFi, Installer Server, Operator, Guest<br />\r\nSchedule gate position<br />\r\nSchedule WLAN modes (WLAN on / WLAN off / access point)<br />\r\nSensor test before each descent<br />\r\nRelay and motor function monitoring<br />\r\npower saving mode<br />\r\ntrip counter<br />\r\nUpdatable<br />\r\ndiagnosis<br />\r\nHousing UV and weather resistant and IP67<br />\r\nStable cable entries<br />\r\n*only in connection with the Android operating system</p>\r\n\r\n<p>connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 tubular motor / 1~ AC motor<br />\r\n1 output for lighting / warning light / alarm siren<br />\r\n3 independent security inputs<br />\r\nFRABA OSE opt. safety contact strip<br />\r\n1.2 / 8.2 kOhm safety contact strip<br />\r\nPNP light barrier / sensor<br />\r\nPotential-free contacts<br />\r\nLimit switch closed / open<br />\r\npre-limit switch<br />\r\nLight barrier for vehicle detection<br />\r\n2 external motor stop contacts for emergency stop / roll-off protection<br />\r\nControl button modes: OPEN/STOP/CLOSE, gate OPEN, gate CLOSE, gate STOP<br />\r\nlight switch<br />\r\nDiscover the parameterization and operation of our demo garage in advance!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Search for the \"Node Devices Smart Home\" app in the store now or scan the QR code -</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating and assembly instructions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Click to download)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>scope of delivery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1x NODEMATIC Smart WLAN gate control model: ND-GC-1S</p>\r\n\r\n<p>incl. 0.75m power cable<br />\r\nincluding operating and assembly instructions<br />\r\nIncl. Mounting material<br />\r\n1x NODEMATIC rolling code radio remote control model: ND-HRC-2S color: red</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes battery, key ring and carabiner holder<br />\r\n1x NODEMATIC rolling code radio hand transmitter Model: ND-HRC-2S Color: Black</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes battery, key ring and carabiner holder<br />\r\nDo you still have any questions? You are welcome to contact our mail support hotline at any time before and after your purchase.</p>\r\n', '', '245.90', '245.90', '', '', '', 'en', 23),
